Interface AadlPackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, ModelUnit, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AadlPackageImpl

    public interface AadlPackage
extends ModelUnit
    A representation of the model object 'Aadl Package'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Public Section
    • Owned Private Section
    • Public Section
    • Private Section
